   <body>
      <context>
         <note>The UPS is configured for dual mains as default.</note>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Move the UPS cabinet and the top entry cabinet to the installation
location with a forklift or a low profile 21 inch pallet jack by lifting
from the sides.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Remove_Kick_Plates_TSK_0000161962.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Install_the_top_entry_cabinet_0000117812.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Only in systems with adjacent battery cabinet(s): <xref href="Prepare_for_Cables_on_the_25-50_kVA_UPS_with_an_Adjacent_Battery_Cabinet_0000114606.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Convert_25-50_kVA_UPS_from_Dual_Mains_to_Single_Mains_TSK_0000110501.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Prepare_the_25-50_kVA_UPS_for_Bottom_Cable_Entry_TSK_0000125402.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Connect_the_Power_Cables_on_the_25-50_kVA_UPS_0000103944.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Connect_the_Control_Cables_for_the_25-50_kVA_UPS_0000161459.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Connect_the_Remote_Emergency_Power_Off_for_25-50_kVA_UPS_0000161515.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Connect_the_Input_Contacts_and_Output_Relays_Option_TSK_0000161513.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Install_the_Kick_Plates_0000103941.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Reinstall all plates and close the doors.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
